PROJECT.NAME: iyMesOrie12-mito
PROJECT.TITLE: Messor orientalis, mitochondrial assembly, iyMesOrie12-mito.
PROJECT.DESCRIPTION: This project provides the mitochondrial assembly of Messor orientalis. The assembly is provided by the European Reference Genome Atlas (ERGA, https://www.erga-biodiversity.eu/) via the Biodiversity Genomics Europe project (BGE, https://biodiversitygenomics.eu/).
